#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong>Odoo for Personal "
"Trainer</strong></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong>Odoo til personlige trænere</strong></"
"span>"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Configure Appointment Types</strong>: In the Appointment app, create"
" types that match your services."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Konfigurér aftaletyper</strong>: I appen Aftaler skal du oprette "
"typer, der passer til dine tjenester."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Client Profiles</strong>: As you get inquiries, add them to "
"your CRM and Contacts."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret kundeprofiler</strong>: Når du modtager forespørgsler, skal du "
"tilføje dem til dit CRM og dine kontakter."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Invoice Your Clients</strong>: Use the Invoicing app to bill clients"
" for completed services."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Fakturér dine kunder</strong>: Brug faktureringsappen til at "
"fakturere kunder for udførte tjenester."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manage Your Calendar</strong>: Use the Calendar app to block off "
"your availability and personal time."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Administrér din kalender</strong>: Brug Kalenderappen til at blokere "
"din tilgængelighed og din personlige tid."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Set Up Your Services</strong>: Navigate to Sales &gt; Products and "
"set up your coaching services."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opsæt dine tjenester</strong>: Gå til Salg &gt; Produkter, og opsæt "
"dine coachingtjenester."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Start Tracking Projects</strong>: For services that require ongoing "
"management, create a project in the Project app."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Start sporing af projekter</strong>: For tjenester, der kræver "
"løbende styring, skal du oprette et projekt i Projekterappen."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Appointment Scheduling 📆"
msgstr "Aftaleplanlægning 📆"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "Det grundlæggende"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Client Management (CRM) 🎯"
msgstr "Kundestyring (CRM) 🎯"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Collaborate with clients on their goals"
msgstr "Samarbejd med kunderne om deres mål"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Convert leads into clients"
msgstr "Konvertér leads til kunder"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a stunning <strong>Website</strong> to showcase your coaching "
"services and allow clients to book sessions online."
msgstr ""
"Opret en fantastisk <strong>hjemmeside</strong> for at fremvise dine "
"coachingtjenester og give kunderne mulighed for at booke sessioner online."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Create and manage your coaching services:"
msgstr "Opret og administrér dine coachingtjenester:"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Create tasks for each stage of a client's journey"
msgstr "Opret opgaver for hver fase af en kundes rejse"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define pricing and project tracking needs for each service"
msgstr "Angiv pris- og projektsporingsbehov for hver tjeneste"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define your availability"
msgstr "Fastlæg din tilgængelighed"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Develop and sell online fitness courses with the <strong>eLearning</strong> "
"platform, expanding your reach beyond in-person training."
msgstr ""
"Udvikl og sælg online fitnesskurser med <strong>e-læringsplatformen</strong>"
", og udvid din rækkevidde ud over personlig træning."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "Vil du tage det et skridt videre?"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model:project.task.type,name:personal_trainer.project_task_type_12
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Udført"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Easily bill clients for your services:"
msgstr "Fakturér nemt kunderne for dine tjenester:"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Encourage clients to book through your Appointment page to reduce scheduling"
" back-and-forth."
msgstr ""
"Opfordr dine kunder til at booke via din bookingside for at undgå konstante "
"ændringer i tidsplanen."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Engage clients with targeted campaigns using <strong>Email "
"Marketing</strong> and <strong>Social Marketing</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Engagér kunder med målrettede kampagner gennem <strong>E-mailmarketing</"
"strong> og <strong>Markedsføring på sociale medier</strong>."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model:product.template,name:personal_trainer.product_product_11_product_template
msgid "Fitness Assessment"
msgstr "Fitnessvurdering"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Follow up on inquiries"
msgstr "Følg op på forespørgsler"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Gather valuable client feedback and track progress effortlessly using "
"<strong>Surveys</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Indsaml værdifuld feedback fra kunder, og følg fremskridt uden besvær ved "
"hjælp af <strong>Spørgeundersøgelser</strong>."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Generate invoices automatically from sales orders"
msgstr "Generér automatisk fakturaer ud fra salgsordrer"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Kom i gang"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to push your quotation building much further and add all the "
"power of Spreadsheet beneath any line of your Sales Orders, use the quote "
"calculation feature."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil gå et skridt videre i udarbejdelsen af tilbud og indsætte "
"regnearkets beregningsfunktion under hver ordrelinje, skal du bruge "
"tilbudsberegningsfunktionen."

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoicing 🧾"
msgstr "Fakturering 🧾"

#. module: personal_trainer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:personal_trainer.welcome_article_body
